The paper discusses content-based retrieval in Earth observation image archives, which involves computer vision (CV) techniques for feature extraction and image analysis. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses indexing and query execution, which are related to information retrieval (IR) and database (DB) systems, respectively. Hence, cs.IR and cs.DB are also likely sub-categories. The paper mentions semantic labeling, which involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, and deep learning (DL) is also mentioned as a possible approach. Therefore, cs.DL and cs.MM are also possible sub-categories.
